commit.message:
configure.ac: Fix a typo in *-*-darwin clause.

2007-06-03  Andrew Pinski  <andrew_pinski@playstation.sony.com>

        * configure.ac: Fix a typo in *-*-darwin clause.
        * configure: Regenerated.

From-SVN: r125301
